{"tid":1771261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣蔡英文其實利用哂香港人既心態","createTime":"2019-12-05T18:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T14:39:10.000Z","uid":307735,"like":6,"dislike":207,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5271dbf296f40c7c2af14950c02c44bf7d41ed","tid":1771261,"uid":307735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得香港人比台灣個蔡英文fake哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利用左香港人反共既穴<br />\n香港人其實唔太知台灣內政 就盲撐左蔡<br />\n仲有人吹話搞個撐蔡英文台灣個d集會 集氣希望佢贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實台灣係小英三年半既統治 都係冇咩進步<br />\n同埋貪污問題 佢做落先知佢衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係香港呢場運動 蔡撐港人 佢大選先有小小生機<br />\n其實台灣媒體好多都幫政府，所有權都係台灣政府蔡手上，將韓國瑜抹黑成親中人士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實韓國瑜以我所知佢唔係親中<br />\n<br />\n佢係有表態先過蔡英文 會接收哂幫助逃難黎既香港學生，好多正面既報導全部比政府com住哂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屋企人話台灣民意係撐韓國瑜<br />\n同埋好多官媒會不停報導負面新聞 <br />\n好既報導得類似民間媒體先會睇到<br />\n所以國際間唔清楚都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如 全部流出既都係韓國瑜話不知道不清楚<br />\n其實佢好快第二日就有解釋翻<br />\n如果你係佢當時個總統都未表態啦 佢而家巿長黎㗎炸 <br />\n你係佢都唔會第一時間就講野啦六月幾個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要我既諗法係香港人冇好好了解就撐蔡 咁樣蔡係利用左香港呢個咁觸目既運動 呃左一啲未夠心水清或者怕台灣變成香港既台灣巿民既票<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先唔好理叫台灣人揀邊個<br />\n但必需承認香港人對台灣政治唔太了解就盲撐左蔡英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企人係當地台灣人"},{"pid":"01292a582abb3f16a8a60bb8cb66242fb67a951d","tid":1771261,"uid":89974,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:02:45.000Z","msg":"我屋企人話台灣民意係撐韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6732f33f0a34fa0cf26572d9d413c30ac8925ec5","tid":1771261,"uid":15703,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"thx 訓唔著 睇完有啲眼訓"},{"pid":"aedacc0234a26cce33120bd562fbf8261611f3d9","tid":1771261,"uid":39181,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"感謝樓主提供笑話一則"},{"pid":"a803972b2df4c2a554920ca2a45f9120a01b0680","tid":1771261,"uid":214185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6732f33f0a34fa0cf26572d9d413c30ac8925ec5","tid":1771261,"uid":15703,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"thx 訓唔著 睇完有啲眼訓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fa1b42d6917de2df1899930a2a77c014055894","tid":1771261,"uid":342786,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:05:54.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜唔親中會行入中聯辦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966d9b1e797232a3954a6d9803edc2d044505905","tid":1771261,"uid":47366,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:06:51.000Z","msg":"最近都有因遊戲關係,接觸過D 台灣人, 有D仲係高雄人<br />\n都係反發大財, 因為覺得韓國瑜實事無咩做,修下馬路咁<br />\n吹水又多過茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.